graph TB
    subgraph "KServe Platform"
        Controller[kserve-controller-manager<br/>Reconciles InferenceService, ServingRuntime,<br/>InferenceGraph, LLMInferenceService CRs]
        Webhook[kserve-webhook-server<br/>Validates and mutates resources]
        LocalModelMgr[localmodel-manager<br/>Manages local model caching]
        Controller -->|validates via| Webhook
    end

    subgraph "Runtime Components"
        StorageInit[storage-initializer<br/>Init Container - Downloads models]
        Agent[agent<br/>Sidecar - Logging, batching, monitoring]
        Router[router<br/>Routes InferenceGraph pipelines]
        LLMScheduler[llm-scheduler<br/>Schedules LLM workloads]
    end

    subgraph "Serving Runtimes"
        SklearnRuntime[sklearn-server<br/>Python]
        XGBoostRuntime[xgboost-server<br/>Python]
        PyTorchRuntime[pytorch-server<br/>Python]
        HuggingFaceRuntime[huggingface-server<br/>Python]
        TritonRuntime[triton-server<br/>C++/Python]
        vLLMRuntime[vllm-server<br/>Python - LLM]
    end

    subgraph "Node-Level Components"
        LocalModelAgent[localmodelnode-agent<br/>DaemonSet - Node cache management]
    end

    subgraph "Custom Resources"
        InferenceServiceCR[InferenceService CR<br/>v1beta1]
        ServingRuntimeCR[ServingRuntime CR<br/>v1alpha1]
        InferenceGraphCR[InferenceGraph CR<br/>v1alpha1]
        TrainedModelCR[TrainedModel CR<br/>v1alpha1]
        LLMInferenceServiceCR[LLMInferenceService CR<br/>v1]
        LocalModelCacheCR[LocalModelCache CR<br/>v1alpha1]
    end

    %% User interactions
    User[User/ODH Dashboard] -->|creates| InferenceServiceCR
    User -->|creates| InferenceGraphCR
    User -->|creates| LLMInferenceServiceCR

    %% Controller watches CRs
    InferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    ServingRuntimeCR -->|watched by| Controller
    InferenceGraphCR -->|watched by| Controller
    TrainedModelCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LLMInferenceServiceCR -->|watched by| Controller
    LocalModelCacheCR -->|watched by| LocalModelMgr

    %% Controller creates resources
    Controller -->|creates| KnativeService[Knative Service<br/>Serverless mode]
    Controller -->|creates| Deployment[Deployment<br/>Raw K8s mode]
    Controller -->|creates| VirtualService[Istio VirtualService<br/>Traffic routing]
    Controller -->|creates| RouterDeploy[Router Deployment<br/>For InferenceGraph]

    %% Runtime usage
    Deployment -->|uses init container| StorageInit
    Deployment -->|uses sidecar| Agent
    Deployment -->|runs| SklearnRuntime
    Deployment -->|runs| XGBoostRuntime
    Deployment -->|runs| PyTorchRuntime
    Deployment -->|runs| HuggingFaceRuntime
    Deployment -->|runs| TritonRuntime

    %% LLM specific
    LLMInferenceServiceCR -->|creates| LLMScheduler
    LLMInferenceServiceCR -->|creates| vLLMRuntime

    %% InferenceGraph specific
    InferenceGraphCR -->|creates| Router

    %% Local model cache
    LocalModelMgr -->|creates| DownloadJob[Download Job<br/>Pulls models to nodes]
    LocalModelAgent -->|manages| LocalCache[Local Disk Cache<br/>PersistentVolume]
    DownloadJob -->|populates| LocalCache

    %% External dependencies
    Controller -->|depends on| Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>Traffic management, mTLS]
    Controller -->|depends on| Knative[Knative Serving<br/>Autoscaling]
    Controller -->|depends on| CertManager[cert-manager<br/>Webhook TLS certs]
    LLMScheduler -->|depends on| LeaderWorkerSet[LeaderWorkerSet<br/>Multi-node LLM]

    %% Internal ODH integrations
    Controller -->|integrates| Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>UI management]
    Controller -->|integrates| ServiceMesh[OSSM<br/>OpenShift Service Mesh]
    Controller -->|integrates| ModelRegistry[Model Registry<br/>Model metadata]

    %% Storage integrations
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| S3[S3 Storage<br/>Model artifacts]
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| GCS[GCS Storage<br/>Model artifacts]
    StorageInit -->|downloads from| Azure[Azure Blob<br/>Model artifacts]

